  <prompt>For PB-020 (notification-tasks-due-soon) and PB-021 (notification-tasks-overdue) read the deployed `sprk_configjson` via MCP `read_query` and compare against the canonical repo JSON at `projects/spaarke-daily-update-service/notes/playbooks/notification-tasks-{due-soon,overdue}.json`. Note: these playbooks are flagged in the spec as needing W1 expansion to membership-scope (FR-7) — repo JSON files will be edited by W1 tasks 022/023 to add a LookupUserMembership parallel branch. THIS task only documents the CURRENT state (pre-W1) for reconciliation baseline. Document deployed-vs-repo divergence + current ActionType 52 presence (or absence) in `notes/audit/013-pb-020-021.md`.</prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Follow ADRs strictly. JPS playbook auditor — pre-migration state capture.</role>

